subject: Gymnastics
lead_paragraph: Chellsie Memmel, the 2005 world all-around gymnastics champion, will compete at the Good Luck Beijing Invitational later this month with hopes of a return for the 2008 Olympics.Memmel will compete in individual and all-around events in the meet.In 2005, Memmel became the first American woman to win the world all-around crown since Shannon Miller in 1994.
